# Handoff Snapshot

Filename pattern:

```text
YYYY-MM-DD-HHMM-<from-agent>-to-<to-agent>-<task-or-reason>.md
```

Example:

```text
2026-05-20-1430-claude-to-codex-task-02.md
```

Size rule:

- Target: 80 - 150 lines.
- Maximum: 250 lines.
- Do not paste full logs, full diffs, full spec, full plan, or long tracebacks.
- Put large outputs in `docs/handoffs/artifacts/` and reference the path.
- Add one row to `docs/HANDOFF_INDEX.md`.

